snippet.textDisplay: this song meant so so so much to me..if you  played this in front of  (me)five years ago I would have teared up ohhh goshh love makes you feel so many thingssss it's an emotional rollercoaster ....and on the other hand the other one gives zero fucks about your feeling that shit hurts so bad  and whenever i listen to these beats this voice this music ...this is nostalgic ..i still get teary while listening to this reminds me how i was ready to take any risk fight everyone for this specific person who never considered my feelings lol ..at the end of the day i felt like a clown this is demoralizing but hey im here to listen to this song again ..love never fades especially first love i will never regret loving just the regret is that i loved you waited 5 yrs just to say a goodbye and this time i wont cry my younger self was weak and innocent which i am not today..we will cry but never expect shit from anyone .,,incase someone read this i wanna say that you got this ..its all going to be okay..if everyone is failing doesnt make you a loser already ..never be afraid to love its the most beautiful feeling everrrr
